items.description:
This is my first LoRA model, which represents the character "Tang Bohu" from the chinese series "Merry Youth Tang Bohu". Trained with 3700 steps at 100 steps per image.

It works well with the default Stable Diffusion V1.5 pruned, Deliberate, AresMix and also F222 to some extent. Good results with anime models like YaoiGen as well.

Try to keep LoRa strength between 0.4 and 0.8, if this value is too high, you might not get the best results. CFG values for Deliberate below 7 give the best results.

No special tags are required, but including "long hair" and "hanfu" results in better images.

Beware that this may produce mature content as well, depending on the base checkpoint.

items.name: Adam Jensen (Deus Ex) LoRA
items.description:
Adam Jensen from Deus Ex series (mainly Mankind Divided) by Eidos Interactive.

Works better with lower CFG vaules (3-6).

Recommended weight range is around 0.4-0.7 depending on the model and CFG vaule, I found that between 0.56-0.6 works decent enough with HiRes fix. Adetailer is highly recommended.

Weight could be reduced when using SD upscale or certain img2img actions.

**Model should know 'wearing coat' , 'wearing armor' , 'shirtless' , 'with shades' , 'without shades' prompts.

**extra propts might be buggy and don't work properly, will require further improvements, add the one you don't want to see in negative prompt (can mess with the weights) if model is mixing outfits, adding 'black bionic arms' promt can help if model is not getting hands correcly when wearing the coat.

Example promts; talojiadamjensen with shades wearing armor standing in a room / shirtless talojiadamjensen without shades sitting in a room / talojiadamjensen with shades wearing coat standing in the street.

Extra Info:

Dataset for the model was around 32 pictures including pictures from the web and in game and manually captioning images.

Released as an alpha, i will try to improve it further on my free time.

Crediting when using this model in merges and such is much appreciated.

If you want to support my work, buy me a Coffee!

items.name: Jeanette/Therese | Vampire: The Masquerade - Bloodlines
items.description:
Character Lora of Jeanette / Therese Voerman from Vampire: The Masquerade - Bloodlines

"Oh, I'm not frightening you, am I, duckling?" -Jeanette

If harley were a mob boss, entrepreneur, bipolar, vampire and an actual interesting character -soul3142


This work is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International License.

If you want to, you can support me on Patreon or Buy me Coffee.

Main Trigger Word - jeanetteVTMB_soul3142 , check examples for other ones.

RECOMMENDATIONS :-

  1. Highres Fix - must, if you are getting blurry and ugly images

    My upscale method: txt2img 512x768 -> send to img2img -> controlnet tile upscale, tile diffusion 2x scale with 4xUltrasharp upscaler and tiled vae

  2. Weight: 0.6 - 0.8

  3. Clip Skip: 2

  4. Denoising - Don't go too high, it can alter a lot of details

  5. For better face's - you can use ADetailer

I use 0.7 weight, 25 steps, Euler a, Clip skip 2 in nearly all my examples with almost same, simple +ve/-ve prompts regardless of checkpoint for my own consistency purposes.

There are imperfections here & there, which i usually leave it in as is, (i never do any inpainting in examples), most of which like hands can be fixed with better prompting, negative embeddings while other like weapons are just bad majority of the time no matter the model as of today.

Some LoRA's are flexible with any clothing, some are not (usually character's with single costume) so keep these things in mind.

This is an unofficial fanmade LoRA, not intended for any commercial purpose and use. All characters and IP rights are owned by their respective creators and owners. I do not own rights to any of these characters.

Created by GeomanticArts and please consider supporting the trainer at geoloras.com

Dragon Quest waifus. Sure. Not the new ones though. Jessica has a very iconic design, and should be widely appreciated. A very old training that could use an update one of these days. But the other Jessica LoRA here is even older, and doesn't seem very flexible. So lets fix that!

'Jessica Albert [Dragon Quest], 1girl, frilly red skirt, corset, purple shirt, bare shoulders, belt with pouches, short twintails' - Example prompt for her default outfit.

The most common issues I found were giving her bangs (add 'parted bangs' to the prompt) and the wrong eye color ( 'orange eyes' ).

LoRA metadata has all the tags used.

The trainer's twitter can be found at https://twitter.com/GeomanticArts

Introduction:

This is a LORA for white stockings, which can improve the texture of white stockings in the picture.

Don't be fooled by the small size of this LORA!

The features of this LORA are as follows:

  1. It's carefully made using a differential extraction method, so the volume is very small. Besides influencing the texture of stockings, it has a smaller impact on other elements of the picture.

  2. All photos are taken with a high-definition camera to ensure the authenticity of the effect.

  3. Because it has a minimal impact on other elements in the picture, even if the weight is quite high, it doesn't matter.

Why make another white stockings LORA when there are already so many? Because I found that:

  1. Existing LORA often contaminates the image. Either it's the clothes or the shoes. Could we create a LORA that only affects the texture of white stockings and does not affect other elements in the picture?

  2. Existing LORA does not differentiate stockings by thickness, style, etc. The overall state is somewhat chaotic.

So, I created this LORA and plan to create a series of different thicknesses and textures LORA in the future, all made from real-life shots, and made using the differential extraction method to ensure quality.

So this might be the best Hosiery LORA you've ever used.

Testing has found that this LORA works better on various realistic models, 2.5D style models are secondary, and the vertical stripe style does not appear on 2D models.

The weight is best between 0.5 and 1.

For 2.5D models, you can even try to open it to about 1.2. When the weight is over 1, if there is no description of other clothes, it will have a certain impact on the texture of the clothes.

これはホワイトストッキングのためのLORAで、画像中のホワイトストッキングの質感を向上させることができます。

このLORAの小さな体積に惑わされないでください！

  1. 差分抽出法を使用して慎重に作成されているため、ボリュームは非常に小さいです。ストッキングの質感に影響を与えるだけでなく、画像の他の要素に対する影響は小さいです。

items.description:
This is the eleventh model in my God series.

You can find all the models at GOD-OF-GREED, GOD-OF-ENVY, GOD-OF-LOVE, GOD-OF-ANIME, GOD-OF-LUST, GOD-OF-JUSTICE, GOD-OF-TIME, GOD-OF-FANTASY, GOD-OF-JOY, GOD-OF-HORROR, GOD-OF-PRIDE, GOD-OF-PUNK, GOD-OF-STORMS, GOD-OF-EUPHORIA, GOD-OF-GLUTTONY, GOD-OF-THE-WEST, GOD-OF-BEAUTY, GOD-OF-SEDUCTION, and GOD-OF-PEACE.

This model is a mix of my FoolKat_GOD-OF-ANIME_V1 model and a mix of lora files to provide a rainbow aesthetic to the images. The model is meant to be a tribute to the LGBTQIA+ community and is for those who are all about inclusion, diversity, and love.

The model has Blessed2 VAE baked into it, so no VAE required.

All of the images I upload for this model are unedited and don't use any special extensions like ControlNet. I do not do any inpainting or img2img to correct errors. Why? Because you deserve to see how the model works without any touchup or special extensions like ControlNet. You can surely get better images by putting in the extra work, which I do for my personal images. The samples are just meant to showcase what the model can do raw with nothing but prompt engineering.

Introduction

A LoRA model of Rupee (Rabbit Deluxe Outfit) from Goddess of Victory: NIKKE. The trigger tag is rupee-rabbit. The key features are blonde hair, playboy bunny, rabbit ears, :d, pantyhose, black leotard, green eyes. 0.6 ~ 0.8 weights are good. The preview images are generated using 1.6 version, 2.0 version Yesmix and MeinaMix to verify the compatibility of this LoRA model on different base models.

Cautions (Must Read)

For anime model,

pls disable 'face restoration' during generating.

pls disable 'face restoration' during generating.

pls disable 'face restoration' during generating.

  • Some preview images are generated using 'Hires Fix' and upscaled using 'SD Upscale'. Thus, if you wanna generate the preview images, pls download the original preview images and analyze them using 'PNG INFO' in webui to get all generating information.

BTW, make sure set this option in 'Stable Diffusion' settings to 'CPU' to successfully regenerate the preview images with the same seed.

  • The training resolution of this model is 1024x1024, so generating resolution must not exceed this range. Try to use 'hires fix' to prevent this problem and help to generate higher-resolution images.

  • For 784mb VAEs (NovelAI, Anythingv3, Orangemix, Counterfeit) users, make sure add '--no-half-vae' in command line of webui to prevent generating black images. See voldy's log for the details of edit method. For high-performance GPU, make sure 'medvram' and 'lowvram' mode are disabled.
